headline: Singapore Airlines: Too Inconsistent For Investment
summary: Singapore Airlines' Q2 FY25 net profit surged to SGD 1.6 billion, mainly due to a non-cash gain from the Air India-Vistara merger. Read the earnings review and why I'm upgrading the stock.
